{"article_id":"w5fiE3KoSIQ3lCUr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Istanbul ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump suggested Monday","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that `` rogue killers '' could be behind the disappearance of Saudi journalist Jamal Khashoggi , after a phone call with Saudi Arabia 's King Salman about the case .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Trump told White House reporters","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that Salman offered him a `` flat denial '' in relation to the disappearance of Khashoggi , a columnist for The Washington Post","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who was last seen in public","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"when he entered the Saudi consulate in Istanbul in Turkey on October 2 .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Later Monday , the Saudis were preparing to admit","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that Khashoggi died during an interrogation","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"that went wrong ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"one","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"that was intended to lead to his abduction from Turkey ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"according to two sources .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo left Washington for Riyadh at around midday","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to meet with the Saudi King on Trump 's orders .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Previously , Saudi authorities had maintained","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that Khashoggi left the consulate the same afternoon of his visit ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"but have provided no evidence","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to support the claim .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Khashoggi 's fiancée , Hatice Cengiz ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who was waiting outside the consulate ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"says","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"she did not see him re-emerge .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"A security officer peers through a partially open door at the Saudi consulate in Istanbul on Friday .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` It was n't like there was a question in his mind .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The denial was very strong , ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Trump said of King Salman .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"`` With that being said , ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Trump continued ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"`` the king firmly denied any knowledge of it .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"He did n't really know --","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"maybe --","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"I do n't want to get into his mind","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"but it sounded to me like","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"maybe these could have been rogue killers ,","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"who knows , ''","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"`` We are going to try to get to the bottom of it very soon , ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Trump added .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"`` But his was a flat denial . ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"CNN reporters saw Turkish investigators ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"including forensics officers ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"entering the Saudi consulate in Istanbul Monday evening .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Saudi officials had granted permission","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"for the premises to be searched ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"a Turkish diplomatic source told CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and police were seen cordoning off the area","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"before investigators arrived .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Turkish officials also want to search the nearby consul general 's residence .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Turkish authorities believe","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"15 Saudi men","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"who arrived in Istanbul on October 2","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"were connected to Khashoggi 's disappearance and possible murder .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"At least some of them appear to have high-level connections in the Saudi government .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"A source familiar with the ongoing investigation told CNN on Friday","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"that Turkish authorities have audio and visual evidence","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"that shows","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"journalist Khashoggi was killed inside the consulate .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"International pressure is mounting on Riyadh","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"to explain the journalist 's disappearance , in a case","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that has created a diplomatic rift between Saudi and the West .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"The UK , France and Germany have demanded a `` credible investigation '' into the events","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and Trump on Sunday warned","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"of serious retribution","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"if the Saudis were found to be behind his possible death .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Saudi officials threatened to retaliate","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"if the US imposed sanctions ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"but Riyadh later softened its tone .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"The case has also caused friction between Saudi Arabia and Turkey ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"which has repeatedly accused the Saudis of failing to cooperate with their investigation .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"CCTV footage shows Khashoggi entering the Saudi consulate on October 2 .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"The agreement","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to allow a search of the consulate","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"comes a day after King Salman called Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to discuss the case .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"The two leaders agreed on a joint working group","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to look into the journalist 's disappearance .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"The Saudi official said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that a royal decree was issued Friday","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"directing the public prosecutor to conduct an internal investigation into the Khashoggi case ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"based on intelligence","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"shared by Turkey with Saudi Arabia .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"The official said","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"although a joint investigation team was cooperating on the ground ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"the Saudi `` leadership had felt","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"that an internal investigation was needed","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"to make sure","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"no stone is left unturned","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"to unfold the truth . ''","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"Amid the diplomatic fallout over Khashoggi 's disappearance , international firms are pulling out of a high-profile investment summit .","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"The Future Investment Initiative conference ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"dubbed `` Davos in the Desert , ''","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"was due to take place later this month in Riyadh ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"hosted by Saudi Arabia 's de facto ruler , Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"The latest high-profile invitee","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"to pull out of the conference","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"is World Bank President Jim Yong Kim ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"according to a person familiar with the decision .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"JP Morgan Chase CEO Jamie Dimon has also withdrawn ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"a spokesperson confirmed Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"US Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin was still due to attend the conference .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Trump said on Monday","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"that Mnuchin has until Friday","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to decide whether to attend .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"`` He 's going to make that decision , ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"The BBC reported","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"that the attendance of British Trade Secretary Liam Fox was in doubt .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"The Kingdom of Saudi Arabia considered delaying the Saudi investment conference until after the investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"according to a source with direct knowledge of the situation .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"It is unclear if that is still under consideration ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"according to the source .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"CNN received no response","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"when reaching out to the CEO , managing director , and organizers of the conference .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Saudi Arabia has found support in a number of Arab allies ,","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"including Oman , Bahrain , Jordan , Lebanon , the United Arab Emirates and Egypt ,","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"which all put out statements Sunday","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"they expressed solidarity with Saudi Arabia .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"The Palestinian Authority also put out a statement of support .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":0,"right":240,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":177,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":168,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":142,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":132,"right":141,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":122,"right":131,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":125,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":3,"right":124,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":4,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"